  <article id="node-951" class="node node-page article odd node-full clearfix" role="article"><div class="node-content">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden view-mode-full"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">
<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">COLD SPRING SCHOOL DISTRICT</span></span></h2>
<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">MEETING PROTOCOLS DURING </span></span></h2>
<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">COVID-19 PANDEMIC</span></span></h2>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.2; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 12pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"> </span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 12pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The Cold Spring School District Governing Board will continue to hold regularly scheduled Board meetings on the second Monday of each month, unless otherwise noted on the Board meeting schedule set forth on the District’s website. </span></span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; white-space: pre-wrap;">Until further notice, Board Meetings will be held via video telephone conferencing software. </span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; white-space: pre-wrap; text-indent: 36pt;">District staff will participate from the District Office located at 2243 Sycamore Canyon Road, Santa Barbara, California, 93108.  However, due to the risks to health and safety, this location will NOT be open to the general public.</span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 12pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Public Comments</span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 12pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Due to the COVID-19 Pandemic, special procedures for public comment will be followed for all Board Meetings during the pandemic.  The public may submit written comments to the Board up until the start of the Board Meeting. Written comments should be submitted to </span><a href="mailto:cgodlis@coldspringschool.net"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; text-decoration-line: underline; text-decoration-skip-ink: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">cgodlis@coldspringschool.net</span></a><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> before 5:00PM of the day of the Board meeting.  Written Public Comments must identify the name, physical address, and an e-mail address where the interested party may be contacted.  These comments will be read to the Board by a staff member during the Public Comment portion of the Board meeting. Comments submitted on specific agenda items will similarly be read during the Board’s consideration of that agenda item.  Once the board meeting begins, no further public comments via e-mail will be accepted. </span></span></p>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 12pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We thank you for your understanding and cooperation as we navigate these very difficult circumstances for our community..</span></span></p>
<h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.30909; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; padding: 6pt 0pt 4pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 15pt; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">POSTING OF AGENDAS AND ATTACHMENTS</span></span></h2>
<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-df5fc420-7fff-c19f-cc9e-c25880049a48"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The official copy of the governing board agenda is posted on the District’s website and at the main entrance of the School, 2243 Sycamore Canyon Rd., Santa Barbara, CA 93101. The agenda is posted 72 hours in advance of a regular board meeting.  Agenda attachments are generally available for inspection on the District’s website. In the event of a Special Board Meeting, the agenda is posted 24 hours in advance of the meeting. </span></span></p>
<div><span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>To read Govenor Newsom's Executive order N-25-20, <a href="/sites/default/files/3.12.20-EO-N-25-20-COVID-19.pdf">click here.</a></strong></span></div>
</div></div></div>  </div>

  
  
